dct_title_s: Netherwood development Plainfield, New Jersey map 1891
dct_description_sm: Map of the desirable builing lots owned by Watson Whittlesey in the development of Netherwood in Plainfield, New Jersey. There is an advertisement notice for land, prices of lots, and sale start date placed by William H. Moffitt, placed in the center of the map. Printed by Chas. M. Kozlay of Brooklyn, N.Y.
Some handwritten notes on the map, and a purple stamp denoted a change in the maps physical location.
